OL,3,CMum's heartbreak as baby's grave
OL,4,Cheadstone is stolen
OL,6,FA mother has described her heartache
OL,7,Fand anger after someone stole a
OL,8,Fspecial headstone from her baby's
OL,9,Fgrave.
OL,11,FCarol-Ann Taylor's son Dylan Sayce was
OL,12,Fborn on March 12, 2008, before he
OL,13,Ftragically died six days later.
OL,15,FThis year, Dylan would have turned 16,
OL,16,Fso to honour his special birthday
OL,17,FCarol-Ann saved money for a headstone
OL,18,Fto be erected at his grave in Bridgend
OL,19,FCemetery.
