OL,3,CMum's heartbreak as baby's grave
OL,4,Cheadstone is stolen
OL,6,FBut when Carol-Ann visited her son's
OL,7,Fgrave along with her husband on 3
OL,8,FAugust, they were shocked to discover
OL,9,Fthe personalised memorial and
OL,10,Fdecorations had disappeared.
OL,12,FThe council, which runs the cemetery,
OL,13,Fconfirmed they had not been removed by
OL,14,Fstaff.
OL,16,FCarol-Ann told ITV Cymru Wales: "I am
OL,17,Fangry that someone could do that to a
OL,18,Fsix-day-old baby, it's just
OL,19,Fdisrespectful.
