OL,6,F"When I come here, I admire
OL,7,Feverybody's grave. I don't touch the
OL,8,Fgraves.
OL,10,F"This is my child and I feel I've let
OL,11,Fhim down and it breaks my heart and I
OL,12,Fshouldn't have to feel that way."
OL,14,FDescribing the heartbreaking
OL,15,Fcircumstances that led to Dylan's
OL,16,Fdeath, Carol-Ann said she only
OL,17,Fdiscovered something was amiss 36
OL,18,Fweeks into her pregnancy.
