OL,6,FShe said: "My son was diagnosed with
OL,7,Fhypoplastic left heart syndrome and I
OL,8,Ffound out when I was 36 weeks pregnant
OL,9,Fwith him. It was a massive shock."
OL,11,FThe option to terminate the pregnancy
OL,12,Fwas advised, but Carol-Ann said she
OL,13,Fdecided to go through with the birth
OL,14,Fto give little Dylan every chance of
OL,15,Fsurvival.
OL,17,F"My train of thought was: 'If he's
OL,18,Fgoing to survive, he's going to
OL,19,Fsurvive'," she said.
