OL,6,F"He went in for (an) operation when he
OL,7,Fwas five days old and survived until
OL,8,Fhe was six days old. He survived 24
OL,9,Fhours after the operation and then
OL,10,Fsuffered a cardiac arrest."
OL,12,FEver since the heartbreaking
OL,13,Fcircumstances that led to Dylan's
OL,14,Fdeath 16 years ago, Carol-Ann has made
OL,15,Fweekly visits to her son leaving
OL,16,Fflowers and ensuring it stayed in good
OL,17,Fcondition.
