OL,6,FHowever, she said that she, along with
OL,7,Fother mourners, had experienced some
OL,8,Fissues over the years with headstones
OL,9,Fand memorials being damaged or
OL,10,Fdisturbed.
OL,12,FShe said: "Since Dylan has been here,
OL,13,Fhe's been damaged quite a few times
OL,14,Fbefore we got the headstone.
OL,16,F"He had the cross on and that was
OL,17,Fdamaged, broken, snapped in half.
