OL,6,F"So it's been hard, but we just wanted
OL,7,Fto do something a bit more permanent
OL,8,Ffor him so people could see who they
OL,9,Fwere walking past.
OL,11,F"People see something and they just
OL,12,Fthink that they have the right to take
OL,13,Fit and they don't. These are all loved
OL,14,Fones here and they deserve to be
OL,15,Frespected."
OL,17,FCarol-Ann wants the council to put
OL,18,Fmore precautions in place, like
OL,19,Fcameras or security.
