OL,6,FBridgend Council said in a statement:
OL,7,F"We would like to offer our sympathies
OL,8,Fto the family and we urge anyone who
OL,9,Fwitnesses suspicious or anti-social
OL,10,Fbehaviour within a local cemetery to
OL,11,Freport it to South Wales Police online
OL,12,For by using the 101 number.
OL,14,F"We would also be happy to provide the
OL,15,Ffamily with support and advice
OL,16,Fdesigned to help prevent this from re-
OL,17,Foccurring.
