OL,6,F"All headstones and memorials
OL,7,Finstalled at the cemetery need to be
OL,8,Fauthorised in advance so that they can
OL,9,Fbe checked to ensure they are fit for
OL,10,Fpurpose and can be securely and safely
OL,11,Ffitted by a registered professional to
OL,12,Fprevent injury or theft.
OL,14,F"While the memorial which has gone
OL,15,Fmissing was not subject to this
OL,16,Fprocess, we can confirm that it has
OL,17,Fnot been moved or put into storage by
OL,18,Fcemetery staff."
OL,20,FCarol-Ann said a kind person had set
OL,21,Fup a GoFundMe page to help the family.
