OL,6,FAlthough Carol-Ann said she was
OL,7,Fincredibly grateful and would put the
OL,8,Fmoney towards a new memorial if enough
OL,9,Fis raised, she stressed that she did
OL,10,Fnot set up the fundraiser herself and
OL,11,Fhas never asked for money.
OL,13,F"We as a family are not asking anyone
OL,14,Fto donate ` we haven't asked for a
OL,15,Fsingle penny when it comes to Dylan `
OL,16,Fbut if people do want to donate we are
OL,17,Fvery grateful," she said.
OL,19,F"If we can get Dylan a lovely
OL,20,Fheadstone in his honour that would be
OL,21,Famazing."
